nodes.text: Vorkeesk was a male Kadas'sa'Nikto who worked for Gardulla the Hutt during the waning years of the Republic Classic era. In 32 BBY, he had a bounty placed on his head in the same year by Watto because he killed somebody who owed Watto money. The bounty was 3,000 credits alive and 1,500 dead, and was claimed by Jango Fett for 3,000 credits.
